      "raw_text": "Washington Water Power Co.\nstockholders formally voted yester-\nday to double the company's cap\nital stock. making total of s10.-\n100000. 1t is announced that the\nincrease is to be issued as needed\nfor Improvements.\n\n\nThe board of directors was re-\nelected without opposition. Officers\nwill be selected by the board\nMarch Is.\n\n\nNet profits from the company's\nearnings for 1906 are estimated at\n$500 900 from gross earning OF\n81 100000. The stock is quoted at\nfrom $3.50 to $3.50, with seven per\ncent dividends on the capital stock."
    }
